dbo.GetAreaName(M.CountryId1,M.CityId1,M.AreaId1) 'AreaName1',
dbo.GetInvoicesTypeName(InvoicesTypeId),
sum(Value),'* '+ max(I.Notes) Notes2,
dbo.GetSuppPersonName(M.SuppPersonId)'SuppPersonName'
from Invoices I
